  "texts": [
    "(16)In addition, the categorial cross-entropy can be utilized as the communication loss function, i.e.,J C = -E K k=1 m k log( mk).",
    "(17)Therefore, the overall loss function of ISAC systems is given byJ ISAC = ω ϑ -θ 2 + (1 -ω)E K k=1 m k log( mk),(18)where ω ∈ [0, 1] refers to the weighting coefficient for balancing the two functionalities.",
    "Training these DNNs simultaneously is equivalent to optimizing all the blocks in the ISAC system at the same time, overcoming the drawbacks of independent design.",
    "Mateos-Ramos et al. [235] modeled the typical ISAC system as an auto-encoder, paving the way for E2E ISAC system design.",
    "Specifically, they used the DNNs to model the transmitter, communication users, and radar receiver, and trained these DNNs in an E2E manner."
  ]
